data.description: **Motivated Seller! Please schedule a showing and submit your best offer!!!**  Discover the perfect blend of elegance and modern living in this spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home encompassing 1,400 square feet of stylish design. The open floor plan creates a welcoming environment with an abundance of natural light, thanks to recessed lighting and hardwood floors throughout.  Crown molding and meticulous attention to detail add a sense of refinement throughout the home.  The electric fireplace adds warmth and character to the living area, making it the ideal space for cozy gatherings. With a large rear deck accessible through sliding doors off the dining room, you can enjoy outdoor living and entertaining. The front yard provides a welcoming entrance, additional entertaining space, and a view of the lovely, tree lined street.   The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring bright white shaker-style cabinets, hexagon tile backsplash, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The generous kitchen island is perfect for casual dining and entertaining.   Upstairs there are 3 good sized bedrooms and an updated shared hall bath.  The master bedroom boasts a private en suite bathroom, adding a touch of luxury to your everyday routine. Each bedroom includes ceiling fans for your comfort.   The finished basement offers versatile space, complete with plush carpeting and a convenient powder room.  The basement also features access to the garage and the laundry area. No more having to look for parking or schlepping it down to the laundromat! If you don't want to park in the garage, it doubles as additional storage space as well!  Other features of this home include central air for climate control and the previously mentioned garage for added convenience. All kitchen appliances and washer & dryer are included, making this property truly move-in ready.   This residence captures the essence of comfortable living in a contemporary style. Make it yours today! Schedule a viewing and experience the perfect balance of convenience and luxury.
